frontmatter.title: Modino.io - V4 Startup Force 2023
frontmatter.summary: On November 20–22, 2023, as the only startup from Poland, the Modino.io team took part in finals of the V4 Startup Force acceleration program. The event was held in the Hungarian capital city – Budapest.
